  "instructions": [
    "Preheat oven to 375°F (190°C).",
    "Whisk together the ginger garlic paste, honey, lemon juice, olive oil, and orange zest in a large bowl.",
    "Add the almonds, dried apricots, oats, pistachios, salt, sugar, and tamarind paste to the bowl and mix until well combined.",
    "Transfer the mixture to a bamboo tray lined with parchment paper and smooth out the top.",
    "Bake for 30 minutes or until the edges are lightly golden brown.",
    "Remove from the oven and let cool for 10 minutes before slicing and serving."
  ],
